                     <interp inst="def2-732-18630511" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">SAMUEL GOODBURN</hi>(45)</persName>, were indicted for<rs id="t18630511-732-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18630511-732-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18630511-732-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp> conspiring together, by false pretences, to cheat and defraud <persName id="t18630511-name-472" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18630511-name-472" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
